{
  "id": "64cb7cb8b37936001c4d6d49",
  "title": "夏鑪冬扇",
  "created": 1691057337,
  "updated": 1691064973,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb8b37936001c4d6d49",
      "text": "夏鑪冬扇",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057337,
      "updated": 1691057337
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34329",
      "text": "かろとうせん",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057337,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432a",
      "text": ">時期が合っていないために、[役に立たない]もののこと。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432b",
      "text": ">または、役に立たない意見や才能のこと。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432c",
      "text": ">または、今は不要でも適切な時期が来れば役に立つようになること。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432d",
      "text": ">君主からの愛情や信用を失ったものや、恋人に捨てられた女性などを指す場合もある。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432e",
      "text": ">「夏鑪」は[夏]の[火鉢]や[囲炉裏]、「冬扇」は[冬]の[扇]のことで、どちらも[季節外れ]であることから。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b3432f",
      "text": ">「夏鑪」は「夏炉」とも書く。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34330",
      "text": ">「冬扇夏鑪（夏炉）」ともいう。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34331",
      "text": "[https://yoji.jitenon.jp/yojic/1357.html 「夏鑪冬扇」（かろとうせん）の意味]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34332",
      "text": "　出典『[論衡]』",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb91225e90c000003570fa",
      "text": "  [後漢]の[王充]による思想書、評論書であるらしい[yits-khawk'9483.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691062562,
      "updated": 1691062776
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb91505e90c000003570fd",
      "text": "   [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/論衡 論衡 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691062608,
      "updated": 1691062614
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb92775e90c00000357105",
      "text": "   東洋文庫の46、新釈漢文大系にも収録がある（ので、ジャパンナレッジにアクセスできると簡単に読める）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691062903,
      "updated": 1691062903
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb953f5e90c0000006a28a",
      "text": "    [https://www.meijishoin.co.jp/book/b98483.html 新釈漢文大系68 論衡 上 - 明治書院]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691063616,
      "updated": 1691063654
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb91315e90c000003570fc",
      "text": "  [『論衡』の「夏鑪」「冬扇」]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691062577,
      "updated": 1691063249
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34333",
      "text": " [松尾芭蕉]の「[許六別離の詞]（[柴門の辞]、[柴門辞]）」にもこの言葉がある",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34334",
      "text": "　　[https://www2.yamanashi-ken.ac.jp/~itoyo/basho/tanpen/saimonji.htm 許六別離の詞（柴門の辞）]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb9a715e90c00000ac715c",
      "text": " 　　[藤原俊成]（[釈阿]）と[西行]を上げている[yits-khawk'9483.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691064945,
      "updated": 1691064973
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34335",
      "text": "　　[https://detail.chiebukuro.yahoo.co.jp/qa/question_detail/q1170524956 柴門の辞(許六離別の詞)の現代語訳わかる人お願いします。 - 『許六離別... - Yahoo!知恵袋]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691057338,
      "updated": 1691057338
    },
    {
      "id": "64cb7cb9e600350000b34337",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
